2246  {
2247  public:
2248  ClosureHandler (typename DepthSense::GenericFunctionHandler<DepthSense::Interface, PropertyChangedData, void (*) (DepthSense::Interface obj, DepthSense::PropertyBase property, ClosureDataType closureData)>::Function closure, ClosureDataType closureData)
2249  : DepthSense::GenericFunctionHandler<DepthSense::Interface, PropertyChangedData, void (*) (DepthSense::Interface obj, DepthSense::PropertyBase property, ClosureDataType closureData)>(closure), _closureData(closureData)
2250  {
2251  }

2253  {

2255  }

2264  : DepthSense::GenericMethodHandler<DepthSense::Interface, PropertyChangedData, ObjectType, void (ObjectType::*) (DepthSense::Interface obj, DepthSense::PropertyBase property)>(obj, method)
2265  {
2266  }

2270  }

18838  publicData.ambientMap = data.ambientMap;
18839  (_obj->*_method)(obj, publicData);
18840  }

18846  }
